1
00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:03,640
Little Fox.

2
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:14,560
Bat saw something brown.

3
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:31,880
He went to tell Cow.

4
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:39,320
I saw something brown. Said Bat.

5
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:44,400
Is it a hat? Said Cow.

6
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:53,120
It is not a hat. Said Bat.

7
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:56,480
He went to Pig.

8
00:00:57,160 --> 00:01:00,080
I saw something brown and hard. Said

9
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,200
Bat.

10
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:04,480
It's not a hat.

11
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:09,000
Is it a box? Said Pig. A box is brown

12
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,640
and hard.

13
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:18,840
It is not a box. Said Bat.

14
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:22,040
Bat went to Cat.

15
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:25,560
I saw something in the barn. Said Bat.

16
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:30,080
It is brown and hard and small.

17
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,440
It is not a hat or a box.

18
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:44,440
Is it a rock? Said Cat.

19
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:47,840
A rock is brown and hard.

20
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:53,280
A rock can be small, too. Cat said.

21
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:59,040
It is not a rock. Said Bat.

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:06,640
Bat went back to the barn.

23
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:14,920
What was this thing?

24
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:29,640
Come look at this thing. Said Bat.

25
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,640
It is not a hat.

26
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,720
It is not a box.

27
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:37,400
It is not a rock. Said Bat.

28
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,000
It is brown.

29
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,560
It is hard.

30
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:44,160
And it is small. Said Bat.

31
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:47,680
Can you tell me what it is?

32
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:58,080
They all went into the barn.

33
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:02,640
The thing is over there. Said Bat.

34
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:06,520
They went to the spot.

35
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:09,240
They looked at the thing.

36
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:13,640
You said the thing is brown. Said Cow.

37
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:17,640
This thing is not brown.

38
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:23,000
You said the thing is hard.

39
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,680
This thing is not hard. Said Pig.

40
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:30,840
You said the thing is small. Said Cat.

41
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,440
You are right.

42
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:36,600
This thing is very small.

43
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:41,120
Bat flew over.

44
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:48,880
He looked at the thing again.

45
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:56,400
But where is the thing I saw? Said Bat.

46
00:03:56,800 --> 00:04:00,480
I do not see it now.

47
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:11,960
Bat looked and looked.

48
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:22,120
The thing that was brown and hard was

49
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,920
not there.

50
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:33,120
This thing was yellow.

51
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:39,520
This thing was soft.

52
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:43,280
The thing made a sound.

53
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:46,160
It said

54
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:55,440
Cat said Bat what is this thing?

55
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:59,760
It is a chick. Said Bat.

56
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:04,120
It is a soft yellow chick.

57
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,960
I found it. Said Bat.

58
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,600
So it is mine.

59
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:13,240
Right?

60
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:21,840
No. Said Cow.

61
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:26,200
The chick must go to its mother.

62
00:05:55,040 --> 00:06:00,240
But you have something, too. Said Cow.

63
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:04,160
What do I have? Said Bat.

64
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:07,400
You have a story. Said Cow.

65
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:11,760
It is about the thing in the barn.

66
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:16,960
You can tell this story to your friends.

67
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:27,240
And that is what Bat did.

68
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:01,920
Bat flew over the barn.

69
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:05,400
He saw a fox.

70
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:17,760
Bat flew into the barn.

71
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:22,240
A fox is coming. He said.

72
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:25,320
Cat woke up.

73
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:30,240
A fox is coming? She asked.

74
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:33,440
Pig ran into the barn.

75
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:36,960
A fox is coming? He asked.

76
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:39,800
Yes. Said Bat.

77
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:44,200
A fox is coming to our farm.

78
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:50,400
Oh, no. Said Cat.

79
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:53,160
We must do something.

80
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:56,000
The fox will see the hen house. Said

81
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,480
Pig.

82
00:07:57,480 --> 00:08:01,360
It will eat the hens.

83
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:05,640
Let's get dog. Said Cat.

84
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:08,800
He will scare the fox away.

85
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:11,720
No. Said Cow.

86
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:14,000
Dog is sick today.

87
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:17,680
We must let him sleep.

88
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:21,680
We can stop the fox. Said Bat.

89
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:25,000
I know what to do.

90
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:41,880
Pig looked at Bat.

91
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:46,120
Cat looked at Bat.

92
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,640
Cow looked at Bat.

93
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:52,000
The fox is coming. Said Pig.

94
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:57,440
We have to do something. Said Cat.

95
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:02,880
We can hide. Said Bat.

96
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:07,440
Cow, you hide behind the hen house.

97
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:11,520
Pig, you hide behind the tractor.

98
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:15,440
Cat, you hide behind the windmill.

99
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:19,040
Where will you go? Cow asked Bat.

100
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:23,960
I will go to an apple tree. Said Bat.

101
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:33,920
Soon, the fox will be here. Said Bat.

102
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:37,800
And we will make some noise.

103
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:44,960
So Cow went to the hen house.

104
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:54,520
Pig went to the tractor.

105
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:59,080
Cat went to the windmill.

106
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:04,160
Bat flew to an apple tree.

107
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:11,760
They all waited.

108
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:21,320
They waited for the fox to come.

109
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:28,120
Bat watched from the apple tree.

110
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:31,800
Cow watched from the hen house.

111
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:35,120
Pig watched from the tractor.

112
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:38,840
Cat watched from the windmill.

113
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:42,680
At last, the fox came.

114
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:46,040
It looked all around.

115
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:53,800
Then it went to the hen house.

116
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:02,960
"Now!" cried Bat.

117
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:06,839
Bat swooped down at the fox.

118
00:11:06,839 --> 00:11:10,480
Cat hissed at the fox.

119
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:14,680
Pig oinked at the fox.

120
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:19,960
Cow mooed at the fox.

121
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:24,480
Then they all did it again.

122
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:30,400
Swoop!

123
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:32,040
Hiss!

124
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,360
Oink!

125
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:36,000
Moo!

126
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:39,960
The fox ran fast.

127
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:43,400
The fox ran far.

128
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:50,680
"We did it!" cried Pig.

129
00:11:56,839 --> 00:11:59,880
The noise was loud.

130
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:03,160
It woke up dog.

131
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:14,120
"You were sleeping." said Cat.

132
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,760
"So?"

133
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:19,440
"We watched the farm." said Pig.

134
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:23,400
"Thank you." said Dog.

135
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:28,400
He felt much better now.